<br>
Agree completely with that one.  Clerics tire quickly of 'Need Temp please' if not being reimbursed.  I've been lucky and usually group with friends that know the 'rules'.<br>
<br>
I've set hot keys to explain the rules, including ML and split, 1 augment/sweet loot win per dungeon per player, NBG - CAWU, and cost of peridots off top.  If the group bitches about it ( usually pick-up groups when it happens ) I leave the group.<br>
<br>
As a matter of fairness, I do not take donations / peridots immediately before entry or during the hunt.  That way no one person bears the cost of something that benefits all.  When faced with the 'rules', I usually end up Temping the tanks, and heroic bond and Pinzam the rest, at a much reduced overall cost.  <p>Phyxious, <br>
